##########################################
# sshd_config.example
# Baseline hardened config (lab-friendly)
# This is roughly equivalent to lab_secure,
# kept for backward compatibility.
##########################################

Port 22
Protocol 2

PermitRootLogin no
PubkeyAuthentication yes
PasswordAuthentication yes
ChallengeResponseAuthentication no
UsePAM yes

AllowUsers secadmin

MaxAuthTries 3
LoginGraceTime 30

ClientAliveInterval 300
ClientAliveCountMax 2

X11Forwarding no
AllowTcpForwarding no
PermitTunnel no
GatewayPorts no

LogLevel VERBOSE
